text_blocks.text:
Progress indicators:
* the confidence level of the population in the Police increasing by 2 p.p. at the end of 2020, compared to 2019, with the growth trend up to 2023;
* the crime rate per 1000 inhabitants decreases by 1-2% at the end of 2020, compared to 2019, with the tendency to reduce until 2023;
* the rate of deaths related to the number of road accidents decreasing by 1.5 p.p. annual;
* 25 modernized infrastructure objectives;
* the average time of police intervention on citizens' calls decreased by 5 minutes at the end of 2020, with the tendency to decrease until the end of 2023

Progress indicators:
* 10 sectoral development programs approved;
* 20 new anti-hail rocket units with modern installations established by the end of 2021; 20 anti-hail rocket units upgraded by the end of 2023;
* 120.0 thousand ha of new agricultural areas protected by the end of 2020;
* increase by 8 thousand ha the areas planted with soybeans by the end of 2020;
* 10% increase in the number of livestock farms renewed annually;
* increase by 15% in the number of breeding stock per year;
* 50 beneficiaries of subsidies for the procurement of breeding stock and 75 beneficiaries for the establishment/renovation of livestock farms annually;
* expand by 700 hectares the new plantations of fruit-bearing shrubs and strawberry by the end of 2023;
* 30 Local Action Groups established by the end of 2021
